freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Developing styes in my eyes....along bottom rims of eyes. It lasts for a day or two then goes away. A few days later, one will develop in opposite eye. No obstruction of vision or need for medication. Just a little uncomfortable.
Swollen and painful ligament on left, inside forearm. *could be completely unrelated to vaccine but vaccine was given in my left arm.
